Package: niceTrafficLight
Type: Package
Title: Evagene Integration Example - NICE Familial Breast Cancer Traffic Light
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A minimal Evagene REST API integration that classifies a pedigree
    against NICE CG164 / NG101 familial breast cancer criteria and prints a
    green/amber/red result plus the triggers that fired.  Distributed as an
    example; not a validated clinical tool.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.8.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.2.0)
